            <title>[WFLY-2797] Update hibernate to 4.3.1 or above according to HHH-8756</title>
                <link>https://issues.jboss.org/browse/WFLY-2797</link>
                <project id="12313721" key="WFLY">WildFly</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;1. The bug description:&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;a href=&quot;https://community.jboss.org/message/851147#851147&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://community.jboss.org/message/851147#851147&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Named query with JPA entitymanager throws exception: java.lang.IllegalStateException: Illegal attempt to set lock mode on a non-SELECT query&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2. This bug is fixed since hibernate-4.3.1:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://hibernate.atlassian.net/browse/HHH-8756&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://hibernate.atlassian.net/browse/HHH-8756&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So please Update hibernate to 4.3.1 or above according to HHH-8756 for wildfly-8.0.0-Final.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;NOTE: I downloaded the latest nightly-build version, found that the hibernate version is still 4.3.0&lt;/p&gt;</description>
